  "ai_usage": "Use for B2B/agency case studies. Lead the hero with the single best result; add an at-a-glance metrics band; tell the story in Challenge → Approach → Results at a readable measure; include a client pull-quote and a next-step CTA. Keep heading order logical, metrics text-labeled, and prose ≤72ch. Recolor via --accent.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/case-study.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Case Study</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"case-study\",\n  \"title\": \"Case Study\",\n  \"summary\": \"A B2B case study: client hero with a headline result, an at-a-glance metrics band, challenge/approach/results sections, and a pull quote.\",\n  \"description\": \"The structured proof piece agencies and SaaS use to close deals — a client/industry hero leading with the standout outcome, a row of result metrics, a readable narrative (Challenge → Approach → Results), a client pull-quote, and a next-CTA. Editorial and credible.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"agency\", \"content\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"case-study\", \"b2b\", \"results\", \"metrics\", \"narrative\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"beginner\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"Type + layout + reveals. No images (gradient placeholders). Light.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Logical heading order, readable measure for prose, real <blockquote>, metrics labeled in text, focus-visible. Reduced-motion safe.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--accent\", \"description\": \"Brand accent\", \"default\": \"#0e7c66\" },\n    { \"name\": \"sections\", \"description\": \"Challenge / Approach / Results copy\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Add a results chart\", \"Sticky metrics sidebar\", \"Video testimonial block\"],\n  \"related\": [\"swiss-editorial\", \"testimonial-wall\", \"blog-article\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for B2B/agency case studies. Lead the hero with the single best result; add an at-a-glance metrics band; tell the story in Challenge → Approach → Results at a readable measure; include a client pull-quote and a next-step CTA. Keep heading order logical, metrics text-labeled, and prose ≤72ch. Recolor via --accent.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#0c100e;--surface:#121a16;--line:#21302a;--text:#e9f1ec;--muted:#8ba398;--accent:#3ddc97;--gold:#d9b25c;--r:16px;\n    --serif:\"Fraunces\",Georgia,serif;--sans:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--sans);line-height:1.7}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px}\n  .brand{font-weight:800}.btn{background:var(--accent);color:#06150f;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:.55rem 1.1rem;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer}\n  .hero{padding:3rem 0 2rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n  .client{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em}\n  .client .logo{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--gold))}\n  .hero h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.4rem);line-height:1.1;margin:1rem 0}\n  .hero .big{font-size:clamp(2.4rem,7vw,4.5rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.03em;color:var(--accent)}\n  .hero p{color:var(--muted);max-width:52ch}\n  .metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;text-align:center;padding:2rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n  .metrics .n{font-size:clamp(1.6rem,4vw,2.4rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--accent)}.metrics .l{color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem}\n  article{padding:2.5rem 0}\n  article h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:1.7rem;margin:2rem 0 .6rem}\n  article p{color:#cdd9d3;max-width:68ch}\n  .ph{aspect-ratio:16/8;border-radius:var(--r);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),#0e7c66);margin:1.4rem 0}\n  blockquote{margin:2.4rem 0;padding:1.6rem 1.8rem;border-left:3px solid var(--accent);background:var(--surface);border-radius:0 var(--r) var(--r) 0;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.3rem;font-style:italic}\n  blockquote footer{font-family:var(--sans);font-style:normal;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-top:.7rem}\n  .cta{text-align:center;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:2.6rem 1.5rem;margin:1rem 0 3rem}\n  .cta h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;margin:0 0 .4rem;font-size:1.8rem}\n  .btn:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:2px}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:680px){.metrics{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav><div class=\"brand\">Studio Form</div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Start a project</a></nav>\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n      <div class=\"client\"><span class=\"logo\"></span> VERTEX · Fintech</div>\n      <h1>How Vertex cut onboarding from 9 days to <span class=\"big\">under an hour</span>.</h1>\n      <p>A six-week engagement to redesign the account-opening flow, rebuild the front end, and instrument everything.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"metrics\">\n      <div><div class=\"n\">−92%</div><div class=\"l\">onboarding time</div></div>\n      <div><div class=\"n\">+38%</div><div class=\"l\">activation rate</div></div>\n      <div><div class=\"n\">4.9★</div><div class=\"l\">app rating</div></div>\n      <div><div class=\"n\">6 wks</div><div class=\"l\">to ship</div></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <article>\n      <div class=\"ph reveal\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Project visual\"></div>\n      <h2 class=\"reveal\">The challenge</h2>\n      <p class=\"reveal\">Vertex's account opening spanned nine days and five disconnected tools. Drop-off was brutal, support was drowning in status questions, and the team had no visibility into where users stalled.</p>\n      <h2 class=\"reveal\">The approach</h2>\n      <p class=\"reveal\">We mapped the entire journey, collapsed it into a single guided flow, and rebuilt the front end as a fast, resumable experience. Every step emitted events so the team could finally see the funnel in real time, and we shipped behind flags to de-risk the rollout.</p>\n      <blockquote class=\"reveal\">“They didn't just redesign a screen — they rethought the whole experience. Activation is up, support tickets are down, and the team can actually see what's happening.”<footer>— Priya Nair, VP Product at Vertex</footer></blockquote>\n      <h2 class=\"reveal\">The results</h2>\n      <p class=\"reveal\">Within a month of launch, onboarding dropped below an hour for most users, activation climbed 38%, and the app rating reached 4.9. The new analytics layer now guides Vertex's roadmap quarter over quarter.</p>\n    </article>\n\n    <div class=\"cta reveal\">\n      <h2>Want results like these?</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:var(--muted);max-width:40ch;margin:0 auto 1.4rem\">We take on a handful of partners each quarter. Let's talk about yours.</p>\n      <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Book an intro call →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <script>\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.12});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
